# Card-audit (mtg-948 Part B): Counterspell — scripted counter-in-response.
#
# Closed issue mtg-495 closed Counterspell as WORKING:
#   A:SP$ Counter | TargetType$ Spell | ValidTgts$ Card
#   "{U}{U} Counter target spell." (CR 701.5 Counter; CR 405 the stack).
#
# Wave 1 could only show this via the heuristic AI happening to counter a spell.
# This puzzle drives a deterministic interaction with TWO scripts:
#   - P0 (active) casts Lightning Bolt at P1, then PASSES priority.
#   - P1, holding priority in response with the Bolt on the stack, casts
#     Counterspell targeting the Lightning Bolt.
#   - Counterspell resolves first (LIFO stack, CR 405.5), countering the Bolt.
#   - The countered Lightning Bolt goes to P0's graveyard WITHOUT dealing damage
#     (CR 701.5c) — so P1's life stays at 20.
#
# This exercises: a non-active player acting in a RESPONSE window via script,
# spell-on-stack targeting (`targeting Lightning Bolt`), and the counter +
# move-to-graveyard-without-effect path.

[metadata]
Name:Card Audit - Counterspell Counters a Spell
Goal:Win
Turns:1
Difficulty:Easy
Description:P0 scripts Lightning Bolt at P1, then passes; P1 scripts Counterspell targeting the Bolt on the stack. The Bolt is countered (no damage), so P1 stays at 20 life and the Bolt is in P0's graveyard. Backs issue mtg-495 (SP$ Counter, TargetType$ Spell; CR 701.5 / 405.5).

[state]
turn=1
activeplayer=p0
activephase=MAIN1
p0life=20
p0hand=Lightning Bolt
p0battlefield=Mountain;Mountain;Mountain
p0library=Forest;Forest;Forest;Forest;Forest

p1life=20
p1hand=Counterspell
p1battlefield=Island;Island;Island
p1library=Plains;Plains;Plains;Plains;Plains

[p0_script]
# Cast Lightning Bolt at the opponent, then pass priority so P1 can respond.
cast Lightning Bolt targeting p1
pass

[p1_script]
# Holding priority in response, counter the Lightning Bolt on the stack.
cast Counterspell targeting Lightning Bolt

[assertions]
# Both spells were actually cast.
spell cast Lightning Bolt
spell cast Counterspell
# The Bolt was countered, so P1 took NO damage and stays at 20.
opponent life eq 20
# The countered Lightning Bolt is in its owner's (P0's) graveyard.
me graveyard contains Lightning Bolt
# Counterspell also went to P1's graveyard after resolving.
opponent graveyard contains Counterspell
